"Really? So it never really ended. Just moved huh. Well, if you can't 
beat them, join them."  She smiled. "Let's get going. I think this 
could be fun after all."  She spread her small wings, only a 15 foot 
wing span, and stretched her small dragon head out. "So, which way to 
home?"
